var book = {
	"name": "Ecclesiastes",
	"numChapters": 12,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The words of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17317A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17317A\"></sup>the Preacher, the son of David, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17317B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17317B\"></sup>king in Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17318C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17318C\"></sup>Vanity of vanities, says <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17318D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17318D\"></sup>the Preacher,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17318E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17318E\"></sup>vanity of vanities! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17318F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17318F\"></sup>All is vanity.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17319G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17319G\"></sup>What <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17319H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17319H\"></sup>does man gain by all the toilat which he toils under the sun?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>A generation goes, and a generation comes,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17320I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17320I\"></sup>the earth remains forever.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17321J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17321J\"></sup>The sun rises, and the sun goes down,and hastens to the place where it rises.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17322K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17322K\"></sup>The wind blows to the southand goes around to the north;around and around goes the wind,and on its circuits the wind returns.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>All <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17323L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17323L\"></sup>streams run to the sea,but the sea is not full;to the place where the streams flow,there they flow again.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>All things are full of weariness;a man cannot utter it;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17324M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17324M\"></sup>the eye is not satisfied with seeing,nor the ear filled with hearing.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17325N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17325N\"></sup>What has been is what will be,and what has been done is what will be done,and there is nothing new under the sun.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Is there a thing of which it is said,“See, this is new”?It has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17326O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17326O\"></sup>alreadyin the ages before us.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>There is no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17327P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17327P\"></sup>remembrance of former things,nor will there be any remembranceof later things yet to beamong those who come after.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17328Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17328Q\"></sup>the Preacher have been king over Israel in Jerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17329R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17329R\"></sup>applied my heart to seek and to search out by wisdom all that is done under heaven. It is an unhappy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17329S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17329S\"></sup>business that God has given to the children of man to be busy with.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I have seen everything that is done under the sun, and behold, all is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17330T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17330T\"></sup>vanity and a striving after wind.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17331U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17331U\"></sup>What is crooked cannot be made straight,and what is lacking cannot be counted.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I said in my heart, “I have acquired great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17332V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17332V\"></sup>wisdom, surpassing all who were over Jerusalem before me, and my heart has had great experience of wisdom and knowledge.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17333W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17333W\"></sup>applied my heart to know wisdom and to know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17333X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17333X\"></sup>madness and folly. I perceived that this also is but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17333Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17333Y\"></sup>a striving after wind.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17334Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17334Z\"></sup>in much wisdom is much vexation,and he who increases knowledge increases sorrow."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17335A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17335A\"></sup>said in my heart, “Come now, I will test you with pleasure; enjoy yourself.” But behold, this also was vanity.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17336B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17336B\"></sup>said of laughter, “It is mad,” and of pleasure, “What use is it?”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17337C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17337C\"></sup>searched with my heart how to cheer my body with wine—my heart still guiding me with wisdom—and how to lay hold on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17337D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17337D\"></sup>folly, till I might see what was good for the children of man to do under heaven during the few days of their life.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I made great works. I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17338E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17338E\"></sup>built houses and planted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17338F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17338F\"></sup>vineyards for myself.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I made myself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17339G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17339G\"></sup>gardens and parks, and planted in them all kinds of fruit trees.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I made myself pools from which to water the forest of growing trees.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I bought male and female slaves, and had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17341H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17341H\"></sup>slaves who were born in my house. I had also great possessions of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17341I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17341I\"></sup>herds and flocks, more than any who had been before me in Jerusalem.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I also gathered for myself silver and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17342J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17342J\"></sup>gold and the treasure of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17342K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17342K\"></sup>kings and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17342L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17342L\"></sup>provinces. I got <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17342M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17342M\"></sup>singers, both men and women, and many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17342N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17342N\"></sup>concubines, the delight of the sons of man.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So I became great and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17343O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17343O\"></sup>surpassed all who were before me in Jerusalem. Also my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17343P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17343P\"></sup>wisdom remained with me.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And whatever my eyes desired I did not keep from them. I kept my heart from no pleasure, for my heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17344Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17344Q\"></sup>found pleasure in all my toil, and this was my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17344R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17344R\"></sup>reward for all my toil.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I considered all that my hands had done and the toil I had expended in doing it, and behold, all was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17345S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17345S\"></sup>vanity and a striving after wind, and there was nothing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17345T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17345T\"></sup>to be gained under the sun.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17346U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17346U\"></sup>So I turned to consider <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17346V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17346V\"></sup>wisdom and madness and folly. For what can the man do who comes after the king? Only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17346W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17346W\"></sup>what has already been done.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then I saw that there is more gain in wisdom than in folly, as there is more gain in light than in darkness.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17348X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17348X\"></sup>The wise person has his eyes in his head, but the fool walks in darkness. And yet I perceived that the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17348Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17348Y\"></sup>same event happens to all of them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then I said in my heart, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17349Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17349Z\"></sup>“What happens to the fool will happen to me also. Why then have I been so very wise?” And I said in my heart that this also is vanity.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For of the wise as of the fool there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17350AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17350AA\"></sup>no enduring remembrance, seeing that in the days to come all will have been long forgotten. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17350AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17350AB\"></sup>How the wise dies just like the fool!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So I hated life, because what is done under the sun was grievous to me, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17351AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17351AC\"></sup>all is vanity and a striving after wind.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I hated <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17352AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17352AD\"></sup>all my toil in which I toil under the sun, seeing that I must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17352AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17352AE\"></sup>leave it to the man who will come after me,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and who knows whether he will be wise or a fool? Yet he will be master of all for which I toiled and used my wisdom under the sun. This also is vanity.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>So I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17354AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17354AF\"></sup>turned about and gave my heart up to despair <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17354AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17354AG\"></sup>over all the toil of my labors under the sun,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>because sometimes a person who has toiled with wisdom and knowledge and skill must leave everything to be enjoyed by someone who did not toil for it. This also is vanity and a great evil.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>What has a man from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17356AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17356AH\"></sup>all the toil and striving of heart with which he toils beneath the sun?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17357AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17357AI\"></sup>all his days are full of sorrow, and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17357AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17357AJ\"></sup>work is a vexation. Even in the night his heart does not rest. This also is vanity.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17358AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17358AK\"></sup>There is nothing better for a person than that he should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17358AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17358AL\"></sup>eat and drink and find enjoyment in his toil. This also, I saw, is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17358AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17358AM\"></sup>from the hand of God,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>for apart from him who can eat or who can have enjoyment?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For to the one who pleases him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17360AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17360AN\"></sup>God has given wisdom and knowledge and joy, but to the sinner he has given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17360AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17360AO\"></sup>the business of gathering and collecting, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17360AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17360AP\"></sup>only to give to one who pleases God. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17360AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17360AQ\"></sup>This also is vanity and a striving after wind."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>For everything there is a season, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17361A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17361A\"></sup>a time for every matter under heaven:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>a time to be born, and a time to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17362B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17362B\"></sup>die;a time to plant, and a time to pluck up what is planted;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>a time to kill, and a time to heal;a time to break down, and a time to build up;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>a time to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17364C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17364C\"></sup>weep, and a time to laugh;a time to mourn, and a time to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17364D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17364D\"></sup>dance;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>a time to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17365E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17365E\"></sup>cast away stones, and a time to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17365F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17365F\"></sup>gather stones together;a time to embrace, and a time to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17365G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17365G\"></sup>refrain from embracing;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>a time to seek, and a time to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17366H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17366H\"></sup>lose;a time to keep, and a time to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17366I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17366I\"></sup>cast away;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>a time to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17367J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17367J\"></sup>tear, and a time to sew;a time to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17367K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17367K\"></sup>keep silence, and a time to speak;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>a time to love, and a time to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17368L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17368L\"></sup>hate;a time for war, and a time for peace.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>What <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17369M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17369M\"></sup>gain has the worker from his toil?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I have seen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17370N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17370N\"></sup>the business that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17370O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17370O\"></sup>God has given to the children of man to be busy with.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17371P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17371P\"></sup>made everything beautiful in its time. Also, he has put eternity into man's heart, yet so that he cannot <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17371Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17371Q\"></sup>find out what God has done from the beginning to the end.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I perceived that there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17372R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17372R\"></sup>nothing better for them than to be joyful and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17372S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17372S\"></sup>do good as long as they live;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17373T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17373T\"></sup>that everyone should eat and drink and take pleasure in all his toil—this is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17373U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17373U\"></sup>God's gift to man.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I perceived that whatever God does endures forever; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17374V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17374V\"></sup>nothing can be added to it, nor anything taken from it. God has done it, so that people fear before him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>That which is, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17375W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17375W\"></sup>already has been; that which is to be, already has been; and God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17375X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17375X\"></sup>seeks what has been driven away.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Moreover, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17376Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17376Y\"></sup>I saw under the sun that in the place of justice, even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17376Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17376Z\"></sup>there was wickedness, and in the place of righteousness, even there was wickedness.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I said in my heart, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17377AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17377AA\"></sup>God will judge the righteous and the wicked, for there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17377AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17377AB\"></sup>a time for every matter and for every work.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I said in my heart with regard to the children of man that God is testing them that they may see that they themselves are but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17378AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17378AC\"></sup>beasts.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17379AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17379AD\"></sup>For what happens to the children of man and what happens to the beasts is the same; as one dies, so dies the other. They all have the same breath, and man has no advantage over the beasts, for all is vanity.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>All go to one place. All are from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17380AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17380AE\"></sup>the dust, and to dust all return.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Who knows whether <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17381AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17381AF\"></sup>the spirit of man goes upward and the spirit of the beast goes down into the earth?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So I saw that there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17382AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17382AG\"></sup>nothing better than that a man should rejoice in his work, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17382AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17382AH\"></sup>that is his lot. Who can bring him to see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17382AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17382AI\"></sup>what will be after him?"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17383A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17383A\"></sup>Again I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17383B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17383B\"></sup>saw all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17383C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17383C\"></sup>the oppressions that are done under the sun. And behold, the tears of the oppressed, and they had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17383D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17383D\"></sup>no one to comfort them! On the side of their oppressors there was power, and there was no one to comfort them.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17384E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17384E\"></sup>thought the dead who are already dead more fortunate than the living who are still alive.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17385F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17385F\"></sup>better than both is he who has not yet been and has not seen the evil deeds that are done under the sun.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then I saw that all toil and all skill in work come from a man's envy of his neighbor. This also is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17386G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17386G\"></sup>vanity and a striving after wind.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The fool <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17387H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17387H\"></sup>folds his hands and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17387I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17387I\"></sup>eats his own flesh.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17388J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17388J\"></sup>Better is a handful of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17388K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17388K\"></sup>quietness than two hands full of toil and a striving after wind.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17389L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17389L\"></sup>Again, I saw vanity under the sun:",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>one person who has no other, either son or brother, yet there is no end to all his toil, and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17390M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17390M\"></sup>eyes are never satisfied with riches, so that he never asks, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17390N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17390N\"></sup>“For whom am I toiling and depriving myself of pleasure?” This also is vanity and an unhappy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17390O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17390O\"></sup>business.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Two are better than one, because they have a good reward for their toil.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For if they fall, one will lift up his fellow. But woe to him who is alone when he falls and has not another to lift him up!",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Again, if two lie together, they keep warm, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17393P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17393P\"></sup>but how can one keep warm alone?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And though a man might prevail against one who is alone, two will withstand him—a threefold cord is not quickly broken.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Better was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17395Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17395Q\"></sup>a poor and wise youth than an old and foolish king who no longer knew how <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17395R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17395R\"></sup>to take advice.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For he went <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17396S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17396S\"></sup>from prison to the throne, though in his own kingdom he had been born poor.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I saw all the living who move about under the sun, along with that youth who was to stand in the king's place.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>There was no end of all the people, all of whom he led. Yet those who come later will not rejoice in him. Surely this also is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17398T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17398T\"></sup>vanity and a striving after wind."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17399A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17399A\"></sup>Guard your steps when you go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17399B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17399B\"></sup>the house of God. To draw near to listen is better than to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17399C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17399C\"></sup>offer the sacrifice of fools, for they do not know that they are doing evil.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup> Be not rash with your mouth, nor let your heart be hasty to utter a word before God, for God is in heaven and you are on earth. Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17400D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17400D\"></sup>let your words be few.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For a dream comes with much business, and a fool's voice with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17401E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17401E\"></sup>many words.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17402F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17402F\"></sup>you vow a vow to God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17402G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17402G\"></sup>do not delay paying it, for he has no pleasure in fools. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17402H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17402H\"></sup>Pay what you vow.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17403I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17403I\"></sup>It is better that you should not vow than that you should vow and not pay.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Let not your mouth lead you into sin, and do not say before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17404J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17404J\"></sup>the messenger that it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17404K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17404K\"></sup>a mistake. Why should God be angry at your voice and destroy the work of your hands?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For when dreams increase and words grow many, there is vanity; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17405L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17405L\"></sup>God is the one you must fear.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17406M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17406M\"></sup>If you see in a province the oppression of the poor and the violation of justice and righteousness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17406N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17406N\"></sup>do not be amazed at the matter, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17406O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17406O\"></sup>for the high official is watched by a higher, and there are yet higher ones over them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But this is gain for a land in every way: a king committed to cultivated fields.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He who loves money will not be satisfied with money, nor he who loves wealth with his income; this also is vanity.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When goods increase, they increase who eat them, and what advantage has their owner but to see them with his eyes?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Sweet is the sleep of a laborer, whether he eats little or much, but the full stomach of the rich will not let him sleep.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17411P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17411P\"></sup>There is a grievous evil that I have seen under the sun: riches were kept by their owner to his hurt,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and those riches were lost in a bad venture. And he is father of a son, but he has nothing in his hand.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17413Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17413Q\"></sup>As he came from his mother's womb he shall go again, naked as he came, and shall take nothing for his toil that he may carry away in his hand.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>This also is a grievous evil: just as he came, so shall he go, and what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17414R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17414R\"></sup>gain is there to him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17414S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17414S\"></sup>toils for the wind?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Moreover, all his days he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17415T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17415T\"></sup>eats in darkness in much vexation and sickness and anger.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Behold, what I have seen to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17416U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17416U\"></sup>good and fitting is to eat and drink and find enjoyment in all the toil with which one toils under the sun the few days of his life that God has given him, for this is his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17416V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17416V\"></sup>lot.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Everyone also to whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17417W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17417W\"></sup>God has given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17417X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17417X\"></sup>wealth and possessions <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17417Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17417Y\"></sup>and power to enjoy them, and to accept his lot and rejoice in his toil—this is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17417Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17417Z\"></sup>the gift of God.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For he will not much remember the days of his life because God keeps him occupied with joy in his heart."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17419A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17419A\"></sup>There is an evil that I have seen under the sun, and it lies heavy on mankind:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17420B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17420B\"></sup>to whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17420C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17420C\"></sup>God gives wealth, possessions, and honor, so that he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17420D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17420D\"></sup>lacks nothing of all that he desires, yet God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17420E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17420E\"></sup>does not give him power to enjoy them, but a stranger enjoys them. This is vanity; it is a grievous evil.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>If a man fathers a hundred children and lives many years, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17421F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17421F\"></sup>the days of his years are many, but his soul is not satisfied with life's <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17421G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17421G\"></sup>good things, and he also has no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17421H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17421H\"></sup>burial, I say that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17421I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17421I\"></sup>a stillborn child is better off than he.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For it comes in vanity and goes in darkness, and in darkness its name is covered.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Moreover, it has not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17423J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17423J\"></sup>seen the sun or known anything, yet it finds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17423K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17423K\"></sup>rest rather than he.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Even though he should live a thousand years twice over, yet enjoy no good—do not all go to the one place?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17425L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17425L\"></sup>All the toil of man is for his mouth, yet his appetite is not satisfied.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For what advantage has the wise man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17426M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17426M\"></sup>over the fool? And what does the poor man have who knows how to conduct himself before the living?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Better <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17427N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17427N\"></sup>is the sight of the eyes than the wandering of the appetite: this also is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17427O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17427O\"></sup>vanity and a striving after wind.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Whatever has come to be has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17428P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17428P\"></sup>already been named, and it is known what man is, and that he is not able to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17428Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17428Q\"></sup>dispute with one stronger than he.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The more words, the more vanity, and what is the advantage to man?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For who knows what is good for man while he lives the few days of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17430R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17430R\"></sup>vain life, which he passes like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17430S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17430S\"></sup>a shadow? For who can tell man what will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17430T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17430T\"></sup>after him under the sun?"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17431A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17431A\"></sup>A good name is better than precious ointment,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17431B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17431B\"></sup>the day of death than the day of birth.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>It is better to go to the house of mourningthan to go to the house of feasting,for this is the end of all mankind,and the living will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17432C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17432C\"></sup>lay it to heart.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Sorrow is better than laughter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17433D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17433D\"></sup>for by sadness of face the heart is made glad.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The heart of the wise is in the house of mourning,but the heart of fools is in the house of mirth.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17435E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17435E\"></sup>better for a man to hear the rebuke of the wisethan to hear the song of fools.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17436F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17436F\"></sup>For as the crackling of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17436G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17436G\"></sup>thorns under a pot,so is the laughter of the fools;this also is vanity.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Surely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17437H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17437H\"></sup>oppression drives the wise into madness,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17437I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17437I\"></sup>a bribe corrupts the heart.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Better is the end of a thing than its beginning,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17438J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17438J\"></sup>the patient in spirit is better than the proud in spirit.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17439K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17439K\"></sup>Be not quick in your spirit to become angry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17439L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17439L\"></sup>for anger lodges in the heart of fools.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Say not, “Why were the former days better than these?”For it is not from wisdom that you ask this.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Wisdom is good with an inheritance,an advantage to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17441M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17441M\"></sup>see the sun.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For the protection of wisdom is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17442N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17442N\"></sup>the protection of money,and the advantage of knowledge is that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17442O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17442O\"></sup>wisdom preserves the life of him who has it.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Consider <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17443P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17443P\"></sup>the work of God:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17443Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17443Q\"></sup>who can make straight what he has made crooked?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17444R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17444R\"></sup>In the day of prosperity be joyful, and in the day of adversity consider: God has made the one as well as the other, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17444S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17444S\"></sup>so that man may not find out anything that will be after him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>In my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17445T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17445T\"></sup>vain life I have seen everything. There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17445U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17445U\"></sup>a righteous man who perishes in his righteousness, and there is a wicked man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17445V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17445V\"></sup>prolongs his life in his evildoing.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Be not overly righteous, and do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17446W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17446W\"></sup>make yourself too wise. Why should you destroy yourself?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Be not overly wicked, neither be a fool. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17447X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17447X\"></sup>Why should you die before your time?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>It is good that you should take hold of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17448Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17448Y\"></sup>this, and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17448Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17448Z\"></sup>that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17448AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17448AA\"></sup>withhold not your hand, for the one who fears God shall come out from both of them.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17449AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17449AB\"></sup>Wisdom gives strength to the wise man more than ten rulers who are in a city.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Surely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17450AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17450AC\"></sup>there is not a righteous man on earth who does good and never sins.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Do not take to heart all the things that people say, lest you hear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17451AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17451AD\"></sup>your servant cursing you.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Your heart knows that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17452AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17452AE\"></sup>many times you yourself have cursed others.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>All this I have tested by wisdom. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17453AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17453AF\"></sup>I said, “I will be wise,” but it was far from me.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>That which has been is far off, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17454AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17454AG\"></sup>deep, very deep; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17454AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17454AH\"></sup>who can find it out?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17455AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17455AI\"></sup>I turned my heart to know and to search out and to seek wisdom and the scheme of things, and to know the wickedness of folly and the foolishness that is madness.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And I find something more <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17456AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17456AJ\"></sup>bitter than death: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17456AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17456AK\"></sup>the woman whose heart is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17456AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17456AL\"></sup>snares and nets, and whose hands are fetters. He who pleases God escapes her, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17456AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17456AM\"></sup>the sinner is taken by her.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Behold, this is what I found, says <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17457AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17457AN\"></sup>the Preacher, while adding one thing to another to find the scheme of things—",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>which my soul has sought repeatedly, but I have not found. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17458AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17458AO\"></sup>One man among a thousand I found, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17458AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17458AP\"></sup>a woman among all these I have not found.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>See, this alone I found, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17459AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17459AQ\"></sup>God made man upright, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17459AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17459AR\"></sup>they have sought out many schemes."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Who is like the wise?And who knows the interpretation of a thing?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17460A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17460A\"></sup>A man's wisdom makes his face shine,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17460B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17460B\"></sup>the hardness of his face is changed.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I say: Keep the king's command, because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17461C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17461C\"></sup>God's oath to him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Be not hasty to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17462D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17462D\"></sup>go from his presence. Do not take your stand in an evil cause, for he does whatever he pleases.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For the word of the king is supreme, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17463E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17463E\"></sup>who may say to him, “What are you doing?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Whoever keeps a command will know no evil thing, and the wise heart will know the proper time and the just way.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For there is a time and a way <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17465F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17465F\"></sup>for everything, although man's trouble lies heavy on him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17466G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17466G\"></sup>does not know what is to be, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17466H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17466H\"></sup>who can tell him how it will be?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>No man has power to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17467I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17467I\"></sup>retain the spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17467J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17467J\"></sup>or power over the day of death. There is no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17467K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17467K\"></sup>discharge from war, nor will wickedness deliver those who are given to it.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17468L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17468L\"></sup>All this I observed while applying my heart to all that is done under the sun, when man had power over man to his hurt.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then I saw the wicked buried. They used to go in and out of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17469M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17469M\"></sup>the holy place and were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17469N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17469N\"></sup>praised in the city where they had done such things. This also is vanity.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17470O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17470O\"></sup>the sentence against an evil deed is not executed speedily, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17470P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17470P\"></sup>the heart of the children of man is fully set to do evil.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Though a sinner does evil a hundred times and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17471Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17471Q\"></sup>prolongs his life, yet I know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17471R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17471R\"></sup>it will be well with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17471S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17471S\"></sup>those who fear God, because they fear before him.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But it will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17472T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17472T\"></sup>not be well with the wicked, neither will he prolong his days like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17472U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17472U\"></sup>a shadow, because he does not fear before God.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>There is a vanity that takes place on earth, that there are righteous people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17473V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17473V\"></sup>to whom it happens according to the deeds of the wicked, and there are wicked people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17473W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17473W\"></sup>to whom it happens according to the deeds of the righteous. I said that this also is vanity.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And I commend joy, for man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17474X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17474X\"></sup>has nothing better under the sun but to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17474Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17474Y\"></sup>eat and drink and be joyful, for this will go with him in his toil through the days of his life that God has given him under the sun.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When I applied my heart to know wisdom, and to see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17475Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17475Z\"></sup>the business that is done on earth, how neither <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17475AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17475AA\"></sup>day nor night do one's eyes see sleep,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>then I saw all the work of God, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17476AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17476AB\"></sup>man cannot find out the work that is done under the sun. However much man may toil in seeking, he will not find it out. Even though a wise man claims to know, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17476AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17476AC\"></sup>he cannot find it out."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>But all this I laid to heart, examining it all, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17477A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17477A\"></sup>how the righteous and the wise and their deeds are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17477B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17477B\"></sup>in the hand of God. Whether it is love or hate, man does not know; both are before him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17478C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17478C\"></sup>It is the same for all, since <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17478D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17478D\"></sup>the same event happens to the righteous and the wicked, to the good and the evil, to the clean and the unclean, to him who sacrifices and him who does not sacrifice. As the good one is, so is the sinner, and he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17478E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17478E\"></sup>swears is as he who shuns an oath.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is an evil in all that is done under the sun, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17479F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17479F\"></sup>the same event happens to all. Also, the hearts of the children of man are full of evil, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17479G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17479G\"></sup>madness is in their hearts while they live, and after that they go to the dead.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But he who is joined with all the living has hope, for a living dog is better than a dead lion.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For the living know that they will die, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17481H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17481H\"></sup>the dead know nothing, and they have no more reward, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17481I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17481I\"></sup>the memory of them is forgotten.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Their love and their hate and their envy have already perished, and forever they have no more share in all that is done under the sun.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17483J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17483J\"></sup>eat your bread with joy, and drink your wine with a merry heart, for God has already approved what you do.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17484K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17484K\"></sup>Let your garments be always white. Let not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17484L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17484L\"></sup>oil be lacking on your head.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Enjoy life with the wife whom you love, all the days of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17485M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17485M\"></sup>vain life that he has given you under the sun, because that is your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17485N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17485N\"></sup>portion in life and in your toil at which you toil under the sun.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Whatever your hand finds to do, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17486O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17486O\"></sup>do it with your might, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17486P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17486P\"></sup>for there is no work or thought or knowledge or wisdom in Sheol, to which you are going.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17487Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17487Q\"></sup>Again I saw that under the sun <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17487R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17487R\"></sup>the race is not to the swift, nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17487S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17487S\"></sup>the battle to the strong, nor bread to the wise, nor riches to the intelligent, nor favor to those with knowledge, but time and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17487T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17487T\"></sup>chance <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17487U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17487U\"></sup>happen to them all.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17488V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17488V\"></sup>does not know his time. Like fish that are taken in an evil net, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17488W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17488W\"></sup>like birds that are caught in a snare, so the children of man are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17488X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17488X\"></sup>snared at an evil time, when it suddenly falls upon them.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I have also seen this example of wisdom under the sun, and it seemed great to me.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>There was a little city with few men in it, and a great king came against it and besieged it, building great siegeworks against it.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But there was found in it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17491Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17491Y\"></sup>a poor, wise man, and he by his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17491Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17491Z\"></sup>wisdom delivered the city. Yet no one remembered that poor man.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But I say that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17492AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17492AA\"></sup>wisdom is better than might, though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17492AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17492AB\"></sup>the poor man's wisdom is despised and his words are not heard.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The words of the wise heard in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17493AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17493AC\"></sup>quiet are better than the shouting of a ruler among fools.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17494AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17494AD\"></sup>Wisdom is better than weapons of war, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17494AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17494AE\"></sup>one sinner destroys much good."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Dead flies make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17495A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17495A\"></sup>the perfumer's ointment give off a stench;so a little folly outweighs wisdom and honor.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17496B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17496B\"></sup>A wise man's heart inclines him to the right,but a fool's heart to the left.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Even when the fool walks on the road, he lacks sense,and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17497C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17497C\"></sup>says to everyone that he is a fool.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>If the anger of the ruler rises against you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17498D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17498D\"></sup>do not leave your place,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17498E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17498E\"></sup>for calmness will lay great offenses to rest.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>There is an evil that I have seen under the sun, as it were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17499F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17499F\"></sup>an error proceeding from the ruler:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17500G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17500G\"></sup>folly is set in many high places, and the rich sit in a low place.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17501H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17501H\"></sup>I have seen slaves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17501I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17501I\"></sup>on horses, and princes walking on the ground like slaves.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17502J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17502J\"></sup>digs a pit will fall into it,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17502K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17502K\"></sup>a serpent will bite him who breaks through a wall.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17503L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17503L\"></sup>He who quarries stones is hurt by them,and he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17503M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17503M\"></sup>splits logs is endangered by them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>If the iron is blunt, and one does not sharpen the edge,he must use more strength,but wisdom helps one to succeed.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If the serpent bites before it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17505N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17505N\"></sup>charmed,there is no advantage to the charmer.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The words of a wise man's mouth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17506O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17506O\"></sup>win him favor,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17506P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17506P\"></sup>the lips of a fool consume him.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The beginning of the words of his mouth is foolishness,and the end of his talk is evil madness.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17508Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17508Q\"></sup>A fool multiplies words,though no man knows what is to be,and who can tell him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17508R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17508R\"></sup>what will be after him?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The toil of a fool wearies him,for he does not know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17509S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17509S\"></sup>the way to the city.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17510T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17510T\"></sup>Woe to you, O land, when your king is a child,and your princes feast in the morning!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Happy are you, O land, when your king is the son of the nobility,and your princes feast at the proper time,for strength, and not for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17511U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17511U\"></sup>drunkenness!",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Through sloth the roof sinks in,and through indolence the house leaks.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Bread is made for laughter,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17513V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17513V\"></sup>wine gladdens life,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17513W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17513W\"></sup>money answers everything.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Even in your thoughts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17514X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17514X\"></sup>do not curse the king,nor in your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17514Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17514Y\"></sup>bedroom curse the rich,for a bird of the air will carry your voice,or some winged creature tell the matter."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17515A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17515A\"></sup>Cast your bread upon the waters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17515B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17515B\"></sup>for you will find it after many days.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17516C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17516C\"></sup>Give a portion to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17516D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17516D\"></sup>seven, or even to eight,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17516E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17516E\"></sup>for you know not what disaster may happen on earth.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>If the clouds are full of rain,they empty themselves on the earth,and if a tree falls to the south or to the north,in the place where the tree falls, there it will lie.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He who observes the wind will not sow,and he who regards the clouds will not reap.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>As you do not know the way <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17519F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17519F\"></sup>the spirit comes to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17519G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17519G\"></sup>the bones in the womb of a woman with child, so you do not know the work of God who makes everything.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In the morning sow your seed, and at evening <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17520H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17520H\"></sup>withhold not your hand, for you do not know which will prosper, this or that, or whether both alike will be good.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Light is sweet, and it is pleasant for the eyes to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17521I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17521I\"></sup>see the sun.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So if a person lives many years, let him rejoice in them all; but let him remember <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17522J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17522J\"></sup>that the days of darkness will be many. All that comes is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17522K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17522K\"></sup>vanity.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17523L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17523L\"></sup>Rejoice, O young man, in your youth, and let your heart cheer you in the days of your youth. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17523M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17523M\"></sup>Walk in the ways of your heart and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17523N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17523N\"></sup>the sight of your eyes. But know that for all these things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17523O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17523O\"></sup>God will bring you into judgment.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Remove vexation from your heart, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17524P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17524P\"></sup>put away pain from your body, for youth and the dawn of life are vanity."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Remember also your Creator in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17525A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17525A\"></sup>the days of your youth, before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17525B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17525B\"></sup>the evil days come and the years draw near of which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17525C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17525C\"></sup>you will say, “I have no pleasure in them”;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17526D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17526D\"></sup>the sun and the light and the moon and the stars are darkened and the clouds return after the rain,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>in the day when the keepers of the house tremble, and the strong men are bent, and the grinders cease because they are few, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17527E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17527E\"></sup>those who look through the windows are dimmed,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17528F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17528F\"></sup>the doors on the street are shut—when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17528G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17528G\"></sup>the sound of the grinding is low, and one rises up at the sound of a bird, and all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17528H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17528H\"></sup>the daughters of song are brought low—",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>they are afraid also of what is high, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17529I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17529I\"></sup>terrors are in the way; the almond tree blossoms, the grasshopper drags itself along, and desire fails, because man is going to his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17529J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17529J\"></sup>eternal <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17529K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17529K\"></sup>home, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17529L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17529L\"></sup>mourners go about the streets—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>before the silver cord is snapped, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17530M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17530M\"></sup>the golden bowl is broken, or the pitcher is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17530N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17530N\"></sup>shattered at the fountain, or the wheel broken at the cistern,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17531O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17531O\"></sup>the dust returns to the earth as it was, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17531P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17531P\"></sup>the spirit returns to God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17531Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17531Q\"></sup>who gave it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17532R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17532R\"></sup>Vanity of vanities, says <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17532S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17532S\"></sup>the Preacher; all is vanity.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Besides being wise, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17533T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17533T\"></sup>the Preacher also taught the people knowledge, weighing and studying and arranging <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17533U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17533U\"></sup>many proverbs with great care.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17534V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17534V\"></sup>The Preacher sought to find words of delight, and uprightly he wrote words of truth.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17535W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17535W\"></sup>The words of the wise are like goads, and like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17535X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17535X\"></sup>nails firmly fixed are the collected sayings; they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17535Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17535Y\"></sup>given by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17535Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17535Z\"></sup>one Shepherd.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>My son, beware of anything beyond these. Of making <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17536AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17536AA\"></sup>many books there is no end, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17536AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17536AB\"></sup>much study is a weariness of the flesh.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The end of the matter; all has been heard. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17537AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17537AC\"></sup>Fear God and keep his commandments, for this is the whole duty of man.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17538AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17538AD\"></sup>God will bring every deed into judgment, with every secret thing, whether good or evil."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;